    "Tool Response Template: A response that follows the predefined format of T u.",
    "It includes a placeholder \"<Attacker Instruction>\" that can be replaced with any attacker instruction.",
    "The placeholder is strategically placed in a field modifiable by the attacker.",
    "For the example in Figure 1, the \"content\" attribute is appropriate for this placeholder, while \"name\" and \"rating\" are not.",
    "For example, consider the user case in Figure 1."
